{"tid":575513,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國律師身中30多刀身亡　公安認定：自殺","createTime":"2018-02-28T08:49:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-28T10:39:14.000Z","uid":35790,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"518a2a2df7b79b82a47a07efaf8ee9147aa1aec0","tid":575513,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T08:49:55.000Z","msg":"中國律師身中30多刀身亡　公安認定：自殺<br />\n<br />\n2018/02/28 15:17<br />\n <br />\n中國江蘇省常州金壇49歲律師吳建生，上周日（18日）被發現身中30多刀死在家中。當地公安對現場進行勘察，認定死者是自殺，有關判斷引發爭議。昨晚江蘇省常州市公安局金壇分局通報，經過常州市公安局覆核，維持自殺結論。<br />\n<br />\n《新京報》報導，通報指，金壇分局刑警大隊接報後，技術員和法醫趕赴現場勘查。勘查發現，現場門窗完好，無外來人員足跡，無明顯打鬥痕跡。當天上午，法醫對死者進行屍表檢查。檢查發現，死者損傷位於額部、枕部、頸前部、項部、左腕前側、腹部，均為密集平行排列、深淺不一的砍、切傷，創口均位於其右手可及部位，有試切創，無中毒徵象，無捆綁約束痕跡，無掙扎抵抗傷，損傷對應部位衣服無破損。屍體右手旁的菜刀上未檢出死者以外人員的痕跡物證，毒物檢驗未見異常，也未檢出乙醇成份。<br />\n<br />\n綜合現場勘查、屍體檢驗、調查走訪等情況分析，警方認定，死者吳建生體表損傷符合自己形成，排除他殺。自殺原因正在進一步調查中。　<br />\n（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180228/1305599/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180228%2F1305599%2F&d=uCRaRgrXmGIwlsKB%2FNEPtZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=b4e0676e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180228%2F1305599%2F&h=864f1ec9\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180228/1305599/</a>"},{"pid":"6bf832b380b61be71bdff37fcaca37c2f73d93d1","tid":575513,"uid":7915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T08:52:53.000Z","msg":"中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a38ffbeffeb944b6ab822942e403902199711d39","tid":575513,"uid":170723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T08:54:08.000Z","msg":"正，仲有咩方法唔係被自殺，而係「自殺」"},{"pid":"7f3766e548f6f000dc93299f628867b9e2f658eb","tid":575513,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T08:55:06.000Z","msg":"神打？"},{"pid":"f3ecbdf10a7f6f7b57ba6cb847a910594429c3e7","tid":575513,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T08:55:30.000Z","msg":"自劈三十幾刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"574b484c792ef42be33075cbd26e02ba2c4df8e0","tid":575513,"uid":34742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T08:57:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a0611e69186df1b7891726e9704482816dd349d8","tid":575513,"uid":81183,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T08:59:04.000Z","msg":"蛤蜉蟈蜻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n律師挑戰權貴， 就係自殺行為<br />\n而身中幾十刀，就係自殺行為個結果"},{"pid":"2039a27584d45b6c4ca8fbbee284ff38b16b8d07","tid":575513,"uid":18127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T10:08:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"672a8a287f10071bb5360108d4de097229e9a874","tid":575513,"uid":38216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T10:39:14.000Z","msg":"梗係自殺啦，傻豬嚟嘅"}]}